# TicketTune does not auto-load .env files and has no TICKETTUNE_* environment overrides.
# Select paths and network permission through the checked-in YAML profile and explicit CLI flags.
#
# A Hugging Face token is optional for public models and needed only for gated models such as
# Llama. Export it in the invoking shell or use the Hugging Face CLI; never commit a populated
# copy of this file.
HF_TOKEN=
